    An implementation of the model object 'Diagram'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Styles
    • Grid Unit
    • Diagram Type Id
    • Connections
    • Name
    • Snap To Grid
    • Show Guides
    • Colors
    • Fonts

    • Version
